# AI agent / local tooling config
# User-specific Claude Code state stays local (agents/, commands/, scheduled
# tasks, worktree metadata, local settings). Shared skills that any agent
# checking out the repo should load are explicitly allow-listed below.
# NOTE: gitignore can't re-include files whose parent directory is ignored,
# so we ignore specific children of .claude/ instead of the whole directory.
.claude/agents/
.claude/commands/
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/settings.json
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md

# Local planning / handoff docs
HANDOFF.md
LUMINA-V1.md
docs/

# Demo recording tooling (GIF is generated output; tape is dev-only)
demo.tape

# Git worktrees for parallel feature development
.worktrees/

